    <p class="text-lg mb-8" style="color: var(--muted-foreground)">Updated March 2026 · 8-minute read</p>

    <p class="mb-6 text-base leading-relaxed">Not all mortgage lenders in Canada are the same. The type of lender you choose at renewal affects your interest rate, your penalty if you break the mortgage, the flexibility of your mortgage features, and what you'll need to qualify. Understanding the landscape of lenders — and which category is right for your situation — is a critical part of making an informed renewal decision.</p>

